        <h1 style="font-size: var(--fs-4xl);">Adventure Outdoors Sports Challenge Excite Teach: Empowering Oregon's Outdoor Enthusiasts</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          Adventure Outdoors Sports Challenge Excite Teach (AOSCET) is a premier outdoor education and recreation center in Oregon, offering climbing, fitness, and adventure programs designed to challenge, excite, and teach participants of all ages.
